quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,1,"Alô. Tazmamt, issekniyen iS ppuûewwben, sinna, ppufeûûlen s$uô Uûwib i Ipwaxebbôen"
  11,2,"Ur âabdet siwa Öebbi. Nek, s$uôeS $uôwen, d aneddaô u d abcir"
  11,3,"Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, steôoâet aS, ad Ifeôôeo fellawen afeôôeo ilhan, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ippak lfevl iS i yal bab n lfevl. Ma twexxôem, nekk ugade$ a ppeppuâqbem, ass ameqwran"
  11,4,"Tu$alin nnwen, ar Öebbi. Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  11,5,"Day nitni, s tidep, ur snefvasen ara idmaren nnsen, iwakken ad ffren fellaS? Xas $ummen s iceîîiven nnsen, day ur Iéôa ara ayen teffren akked wayen d qqaôen? Neppa, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren"
  11,6,"Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ôôeéq is ar Öebbi. Issen tanezdu$t is, tanîelt is. Meôôa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  11,7,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa $ef waman. A kwen Ijeôôeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: \"ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen\", wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"ayagi, kan, d ssêur n ûûeê"
  11,8,"Ma Neswexxeô asen aâaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"d acu iT iîîfen\"? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveôôfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen i$ef pmmaâliken"